Standing out in the crowd

As well as his supreme talent, Depay catches the eye with his large collection of tattoos. The young PSV star even has the inside of his lip inked.

On his left arm, the winger has artwork dedicated to his grandfather who passed away the day after Depay's 15th birthday. 

